{"tid":2019011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔係要保皇贏 我係要黃碧雲輸!!!","createTime":"2020-05-16T03:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T05:10:16.000Z","uid":225100,"like":76,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"33e0539b67b54dae3e20088688a44a38692e74cb","tid":2019011,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">初選一定要趕絕黃碧雲</span></span><br />\n任何追擊一舊雲嘅行動都唔應該被視為分化<br />\n因為黃碧雲嘅存在就係割勇武鳩投票<br />\n就係分化緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲係成個民主黨推出黎代表參選嘅<br />\n責任就係響晒民主黨度<br />\n必須用選票去話比民主黨知呢個決定係錯<br />\n理論上因為咁初選<span style=\"color: red;\">一票不投民主黨</span>係冇問題嘅<br />\n<br />\n但希望<span style=\"color: gold;\">以下3個人可以豁免</span><br />\n1。鄺仔 2。許勇武 3。逃緊生<br />\n<br />\n1同2唔洗解釋啦<br />\n3打制度內就一定要利用佢最資深議員嘅優勢<br />\n可能好多人都唔鐘意佢 覺得佢都係老泛民一員話我同意嘅<br />\n但唔好忘記 當年逃犯條例鬧雙胞胎<br />\n佢係功不可沒嘅 亦逼使港共夾硬黎<br />\n所以佢都有啲手段 最資深議員唔係流嘅<br />\n<br />\nanyway當務之急係踢走黃碧雲<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">踢走呢條分化撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a1e4f0b51b62bc768e152568d88a8cf0d6188824","tid":2019011,"uid":225100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭再出發<br />\n香港要獨立</span><br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴冒生命危險寄語香港人<br />\n街頭 議會 國際 三線<span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQXeSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQXeSo.png&h=c52485db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef7d75a727cc0976c443d359e2867d081e5bbdbf","tid":2019011,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce8d1ff1c7ff7915d6b89ce84fed9f3c8f1884a","tid":2019011,"uid":145273,"like":4,"disli